óŸOarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/to_text.mdŸ@1c2f163dfe200501a0870b08855a8db1a5c6033c4314473ec7d3bff5ce9ea5d6Ætitle: to textë®Examples⁄°Outputs data as simple text with a trailing newline.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [1] | to text
1


```
Outputs data as simple text without a trailing newline.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [1] | to text --no-newline
1

```
Outputs external data as simple text.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> git help -a | lines | find -r '^ ' | to text


```
Outputs records as simple text.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> ls | to text


```
